</P>
<P>
London: min. 13 degrees C., max. 21 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 15 degrees C., max. 22 degrees C., moderate
rain, calm to gentle breeze. 
</P>
</TEXT>
