Oil prices had a good rise on Friday night and the fortunes
were reflected on the market today, with Woodside Petroleum
improving 25 cents to 12.90 Australian dollars.
</P>
<P>
Bellwether BHP rose 15 cents to 16.20 Australian dollars and
WMC improved four to 6.46 Australian dollars while mining giant
Rio Tinto gained 14 to 20.77 Australian dollars.
</P>
