<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Kenyan Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, September 29 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Kenyan newspapers today.
</P>
<P>
Kenya Times
</P>
<P>
-- Rwandan President Pasteur Bizimungu said Sunday the bulk of
his army had withdrawn from the neighboring Democratic Republic
of Congo where it helped to topple late dictator Mobutu Seko
Seko.
</P>
